core.tut.pori.websocket

Class SocketService

  • java.lang.Object
    • core.tut.pori.websocket.SocketService
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    TaskFinishedService

    public abstract class SocketService
extends java.lang.Object
    An abstract class for handling simple text/broadcast to users. Sub-classing this class will automatically add an instance to the WebSocketHandler, retrievable through ServiceInitializer.

        public boolean hasSessions(UserIdentity authenticatedUser)
